---------------------
--- Webpage 'Lottery Info' Specification
---------------------

1. Responsive to Various screen sizes
    - Width > Height screen (mainly PC screens)
    - Height > Width screen (mainly Mobile screens)

2. Webpage contents
    - Shows 8 recent draws with draw numbers, and draw date
    
3-1. Automatic update of draw results
    - Option 1) save to an offline file, update it automatically
    - Option 2) crawl data from external draw result sources when the user visits the page

3-2. Automatic check of update failures
    - If Option 1/2 fails to get valid data, notice the owner

4. Google Analytics

5. Google and